{"title":"Vim","uid":"f801d5c68164878ce99d24cd099b895e","slug":"Vim","date":"2022-04-07T01:59:14.000Z","updated":"2022-04-07T02:16:41.262Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Vim.json","keywords":"Blog","cover":["https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/文章默认封面.jpg"],"content":"<p>Linux vi 命令也就是指 vi 编辑器，它们是一个意思。vi 编辑器是 Linux/UNIX 环境下经典的编辑器。Linux vi 命令非常强大，熟练地使用它可以高效的编辑代码，配置系统文件等，是程序员和运维人员必须掌握的技能。现在的 UNIX/Linux 大都使用 vim 代替了 vi。vim 是 vi 的增强版（vi Improved），与 vi 编辑器完全兼容，而且实现了很多增强功能。</p>\n<p>Linux 开源操作系统内核，我作为一个开源极致推崇者，怎么能不学习使用 Linux 呢? 在下面的三篇博客中，我都在使用 Linux。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://cosmicdusty.cc/post/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95\">第一次深度学习尝试 | Murphy’s Blog (cosmicdusty.cc)</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://cosmicdusty.cc/post/%E3%80%8A%E9%B8%9F%E5%93%A5%E7%9A%84Linux%E7%A7%81%E6%88%BF%E8%8F%9C%E3%80%8B\">《鸟哥的Linux私房菜》 | Murphy’s Blog (cosmicdusty.cc)</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://cosmicdusty.cc/post/Linux%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95\">Linux安装记录 | Murphy’s Blog (cosmicdusty.cc)</a></p>\n<p>我使用Linux不是很熟练，熟练度都是练习出来的，我平时用的大部分还是在Windows上面，于是我决定在Windows上面使用vim，当我转到Linux上的时候，至少对vim不再害怕了！</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.runoob.com/linux/linux-vim.html\">Linux vi/vim | 菜鸟教程 (runoob.com)</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://c.biancheng.net/vi/\">Linux vi命令（vi编辑器）30分钟入门教程 (biancheng.net)</a></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"Linux vi 命...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":574,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"工具利器","slug":"工具利器","count":8,"path":"api/categories/工具利器.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"效率工具","slug":"效率工具","count":6,"path":"api/tags/效率工具.json"},{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":4,"path":"api/tags/Linux.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Murphy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/aboutme.jpg","link":"/","description":"A Future Without Disappointment!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/murphyhoucn","twitter